posting_body: ['COME ON BY FOR A NEW HOME FIND!!!', 'Magnolia Square', 'https://essexapts.info/Magnolia-Square', 'show contact info', 'Come home to happiness and let us help you find your new apartment today!', '*Unit MS033* is available for immediate move in!', '*$500 off your second month!', '* on approved credit/12-month lease term*', 'CONTACT US TODAY TO LEARN MORE AND SCHEDULE A TOUR!', 'Finding your new apartment home has never been easier with our self-guided tours (currently limited to two people per tour), 360-degree online tours, virtual tours and our quick-and-easy online application process.', 'Call us at {Craigslist tracking phone number} or visit {website URL} to schedule a tour online.', 'THE ESSEX DIFFERENCE', '30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee', 'We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee with any leased apartment.', 'If you’re not 100% satisfied with your new home, we’ll help you transfer to a comparable home within the same community or you can choose to terminate your lease.*', 'On-Site Maintenance', 'From replacing a light bulb to fixing an after-hours water leak, we are here for our residents.', 'Our maintenance team provides on-site support to keep your apartment and our community running smoothly.', 'We’re even available 24/7 for emergency issues that might arise.', 'At Essex, we’ve got you covered.']
